data.description: Discover an extraordinary opportunity to call Matteson home with this spacious RANCH-style gem! This residence seamlessly combines comfort and convenience. Boasting a sizeable layout, this home features 4 generously sized bedrooms and 3 beautifully appointed bathrooms, offering an abundance of space with a two car garage.  Step outside to your very own private backyard, complete with patio.  Inside, you'll find a well-thought-out layout with two bedrooms conveniently located on the main level. Venture downstairs, and you'll discover two additional bedrooms, offering flexibility and versatility to suit your lifestyle.  Ample storage space throughout the home, keeping your living areas organized.  Enjoy close proximity to shopping, transportation, and all the amenities Matteson has to offer~ Proximity to the highway~ ROOF 2018
